  "description": "<p><strong>国外专利网站Patent Bolt今天披露了一部三星的新设备组合，它的造型和结构让我们想起了华硕的PadPhone：可以将手机放在一台平板基座中组合成一台设备。</strong>不过这两者之间的区别在于三星的设备组合后形状像字母T，而华硕的方式是将设备二合一。这类设备组合的概念可以带来更强的性能和更多功能，但目前还不清楚三星会有什么样的具体产品会出现在市场。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ea06fc1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244615.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E5%8D%8E%E7%A1%95PadPhone%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244615.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E5%8D%8E%E7%A1%95PadPhone%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244615.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E5%8D%8E%E7%A1%95PadPhone%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244615.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E5%8D%8E%E7%A1%95PadPhone%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%93%E5%88%A9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244615.htm&